{"3413800": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Hotel Tales", "steam_appid": 3413800, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h1>💖 RELEASE VERY SOON 💖</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413800/extras/4f0bda38cb20c0fc833e6e268aa333dd.avif?t=1775676790\" width=1200 height=600 /></span></p></p><br><h1>關於此遊戲</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✦ 真實飯店模擬器</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理你的時間：規劃輪班，完成任務，並選擇與誰共度良宵，無論是戰爭女神還是酒吧裡的幽靈女郎。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >為客人服務的迷你遊戲：從辦理入住手續到…懲罰違規者。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >改善與角色的關係，解鎖專屬情色場景、秘密，甚至全新任務。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413800/extras/143ce63c1d50fccd3af374f60768c8b0.poster.avif?t=1775676790\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413800/extras/143ce63c1d50fccd3af374f60768c8b0.webm?t=1775676790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413800/extras/143ce63c1d50fccd3af374f60768c8b0.mp4?t=1775676790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✦ 社交探索與陰謀</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潛行、竊聽、分析。每個角色都有弱點、癖好和不可告人的動機。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >從對話、事件和情境中收集「關鍵字詞」－用它們來解鎖獨特的台詞，進行勾引、挑釁或勒索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特殊的「夜間事件」：抓到正在舉行儀式的客人、看到床下有傳送門、聽到奇怪的聲音－你可以選擇：介入或…旁觀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413800/extras/bfac10cda1022f203563ab90dd84